precis:
Enactment of the WTO TECHNICAL AMENDMENTS ORDER, NO. 5 which amends
Supplementary Note 1 of Chapter 4 to Schedule I to the Customs Tariff to
reflect the renumbering of tariff items resulting from the delayed
implementation of the WTO Agreement in respect of specified dairy products.
